3. **Octal literals** (line ~710): Creates TOKEN_INTEGER for type checker validation
4. **Decimal literals** (line ~923): Creates TOKEN_INTEGER/TOKEN_FLOAT for type checker validation

Type checker already had "fits-or-fails" logic from original design - validates range and emits helpful errors.

